spec_data.Name: perl-Log-Dispatch-FileRotate
spec_data.Description:
This module provides a simple object for logging to files under the
Log::Dispatch::* system, and automatically rotating them according to
different constraints. This is basically a Log::Dispatch::File wrapper
with additions.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 08 Aug 2017 10:46:41 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Log to files that archive/rotate themselves
